ZH: 我买了一瓶香油来做菜。
EN: I bought a bottle of sesame oil to cook with.

ZH: 这道菜需要加一点点香油。
EN: This dish requires a little bit of sesame oil.

ZH: 香油的味道很浓郁。
EN: Sesame oil has a strong flavor.

ZH: 少量的香油能提升菜肴的味道。
EN: A small amount of sesame oil can enhance the dish's taste.

ZH: 你喜欢用哪种香油？
EN: Which type of sesame oil do you like to use?

ZH: 这个汤需要放一勺香油。
EN: This soup needs a spoonful of sesame oil.

ZH: 香油是亚洲烹饪中常用的调味品。
EN: Sesame oil is a commonly used seasoning in Asian cooking.

ZH: 纯正的香油是从芝麻中提取的。
EN: Authentic sesame oil is extracted from sesame seeds.

ZH: 香油有助于增加菜肴的香气。
EN: Sesame oil helps to enhance the aroma of dishes.

ZH: 加一点香油可以使菜肴更顺滑。
EN: Adding a little sesame oil can make dishes smoother.

ZH: 你用了太多香油，菜肴会变得油腻。
EN: You used too much sesame oil, the dish will become greasy.

ZH: 我喜欢用花生香油来炒菜。
EN: I like to use peanut sesame oil for stir-frying.

ZH: 香油可以增添菜肴的层次感。
EN: Sesame oil can add layers of flavor to dishes.

ZH: 这个蘸酱需要加一点点香油。
EN: This dipping sauce needs a little bit of sesame oil.

ZH: 倒一些香油在凉拌菜上。
EN: Pour some sesame oil over the cold dish.

ZH: 这款香油是特别选用的，质量很好。
EN: This brand of sesame oil is specially selected and of high quality.

ZH: 加一勺香油，使味道更浓郁。
EN: Add a spoonful of sesame oil to make the taste richer.

ZH: 用香油煎一些小龙虾可以增加风味。
EN: Frying crayfish with sesame oil can enhance the flavor.

ZH: 这道糖醋排骨需要加一点点香油。
EN: This sweet and sour pork dish needs a little bit of sesame oil.

ZH: 加一点点香油在炒面上，会更好吃。
EN: Adding a little bit of sesame oil to stir-fried noodles can make them more delicious.
